text.section:
The proposed lease area may not be located:
Within a minimum of 50 feet of shoreline or any pier without the written permission of the riparian owner at the time of application for the lease;
Within 150 feet of the public shellfish fishery or a registered pound net site;
Within 150 feet of an oyster reserve or any Yates Bar located in an oyster sanctuary;
Within 150 feet of a federal navigational channel;
In any creek, cove, bay, or inlet less than 300 feet wide at its mouth at mean low tide;
In an SAV Protection Zone; or
In a setback or buffer from the Assateague Island National Seashore established by the Department.
